txt.en: A report to pinned to the board, signed by Bregdal:\n\n'Trolls carting waggons of supplies have been spotted in Dâr Mauzur, in Talath Úrui. A brave adventurer is needed to destroy these waggons and defeat these trolls.'

'I have returned from scouting Dâr Mauzur and there are Orcs and the like gathering there in numbers. Trolls seem to be carting in supplies. If you find yourself in Dâr Mauzur, it may be useful to destroy their waggons and defeat the trolls that pull them.'
Defeated Mordor Pullers and destroyed wagons.
Bregdal has asked you to defeat Mordor Pullers in Dâr Mauzur and destroy tools and waggons.
You have done much to aid the efforts in Mordor.
Bregdal, a soldier of Gondor, has scouted Talath Úrui and found a fortified enemy encampment within the sprawling wreckage of Dâr Mauzur.
Defeat Mordor Pullers in Dâr Mauzur ([placeholder]/[placeholder])
